  "commentary": "With SPX at 6922 sitting between the flip at 6858 and max positive gamma at 6950, dealers are currently in modest sell mode as they hedge their long gamma positions against this morning's rally. The thick positive gamma walls at 6950 (+12.6B) and 7000 (+10.1B) create strong resistance overhead, while the PIN regime should provide support on any dips back toward 6900 (+9.3B gamma). Watch for rejection at the 6950 level where dealers will aggressively sell gamma, and potential mean reversion back toward the 6900-6925 zone given the stabilizing regime dynamics.\n\nBottom line: expect the market to grind sideways between 6900-6950 with resistance building toward 6950.",
